@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About EventEase</PageTitle>


<div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-center">About EventEase</h1>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
        <p class="lead">
            The <strong>EventEase</strong> project was developed by <strong>Waleed Ali Sarwar</strong> as part of the
            <strong>Blazor for Front-End Development Course</strong>, a module in the
            <strong>Microsoft Front-End Developer Professional Certificate</strong> program. This project showcases
