<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
        <h2 class="h3 mb-3 mt-5 fw-bold">Key Features</h2>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Interactive Registration Form</strong>:
                A user-friendly form powered by Blazor's <code>DataAnnotationsValidator</code>, capturing attendee
                details with validation.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>State Management via SessionState</strong>:
                Tracks user sessions and attendees dynamically using Blazor's scoped services.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Dynamic Event List</strong>:
                Displays event data fetched from a JSON file using an <code>EventService</code> for scalability.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Event Details Page</strong>:
                Dynamically displays comprehensive event details and a tabular attendee list.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>Responsive Design</strong>:
                Ensures compatibility across all devices using Bootstrap 5's responsive grid.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

